&lt;div topic=&quot;Autohypnosis&quot; level=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Autohypnosis (Wis; Trained Only; Psionic)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Description&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt; You have trained your mind to gain mastery over your body and the mind's own deepest capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Check&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt; The DC and the effect of a successful check depend on the task you attempt.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;

