&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;3&quot; curcol=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
&lt;td&gt;20&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Grappling or pinned. (You can manifest powers normally unless you fail your Concentration check.)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;

