      &lt;div topic=&quot;Reduce Teaching/Training&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Reduce Teaching/Training:&lt;/b&gt; Normally, teaching or training a creature requires two months of time. A character can accelerate the process of teaching or training a creature, reducing the time required to the listed time, by adding the DC modifier to the base DC for teaching or training the creature. A character can't reduce the required time to less than 1 minute.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p/&gt;&lt;p/&gt;
