&lt;div topic=&quot;Handle Animal&quot; level=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Handle Animal (Cha; Trained Only)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Check&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt; The DC depends on what you are trying to do.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p/&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;

