full_text:
&lt;div topic=&quot;Open Lock&quot; level=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Open Lock (Dex; Trained Only)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Description&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt; Attempting an Open Lock check without a set of thieves' tools imposes a -2 circumstance penalty on the check, even if a simple tool is employed. If you use masterwork thieves' tools, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus on the check.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Check&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt; The DC for opening a lock varies from 20 to 40, depending on the quality of the lock, as given on the table below.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p/&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;

