&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Special&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Special:&lt;/b&gt; If you have the Nimble Fingers feat, you get a +2 bonus on Open Lock checks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Untrained&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Untrained:&lt;/b&gt; You cannot pick locks untrained, but you might successfully force them open.&lt;/p&gt;
