skill_check:
&lt;p&gt; Typical riding actions don't require checks. You can saddle, mount, ride, and dismount from a mount without a problem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following tasks do require checks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p/&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;

