&lt;div topic=&quot;Ride&quot; level=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Ride (Dex)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Description&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt; If you attempt to ride a creature that is ill suited as a mount, you take a -5 penalty on your Ride checks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Check&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt; Typical riding actions don't require checks. You can saddle, mount, ride, and dismount from a mount without a problem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following tasks do require checks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p/&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;

