&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Action&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Action:&lt;/b&gt; Not applicable. Tumbling is part of movement, so a Tumble check is part of a move action.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Try Again&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Try Again:&lt;/b&gt; Usually no. An audience, once it has judged a tumbler as an uninteresting performer, is not receptive to repeat performances.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can try to reduce damage from a fall as an instant reaction only once per fall.&lt;/p&gt;
