&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div topic=&quot;Synergy&quot; level=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Synergy:&lt;/b&gt; If you have 5 or more ranks in Tumble, you get a +2 bonus on Balance and Jump checks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you have 5 or more ranks in Jump, you get a +2 bonus on Tumble checks.&lt;/p&gt;
